🏠 House Price Prediction

This project uses Machine Learning to predict house prices based on various features like location, area, and other factors.

1 - 📌 Project Overview
The goal of this project is to build a predictive model that estimates house prices using real-world housing data.

2 - 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Jupyter Notebook

3 - 📂 Project Structure
- Data/ → dataset used
- notebooks/ → analysis & model building

4 - 🚀 Features
- Data Cleaning
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Model Training
- Prediction

5 - 📊 Output
Model predicts house prices based on input features.

6 - Future Improvements
- Add more advanced models
- Deploy as a web app

